  first demonstrated by chemistry teacher lee marek on the late show with david letterman in 1999 , and later popularized in a june 2006   viral internet video by eepybird , a mentos mint expedites a rapid release of carbon dioxide when dropped into a carbonated liquid , such as a soft drink .

science fact : as seen on the internet , dropping mentos into diet soda releases this gas out of suspension , creating a geyser

